{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20260421/s00024/74a909661ab1493e83aed4123a42484f.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:1em\"><div id=\"upper\"><p>墨西哥首都墨西哥城附近的世界文化遺產特奧蒂瓦坎（Teotihuacan）金字塔景區周一（20日）上午發生奪命槍擊案。路透社片段聽到現場有槍聲，見到槍手，多人躺臥在金字塔上［詳情］。（路透社） </p></div>&#13;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t&#13;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-22T00:52:55.149915+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":95,"images":1,"source":"明報 消閒","fallback":"none"}}